beyond the class?

831
00:46:08,120 --> 00:46:09,760
No, of course not.

832
00:46:09,840 --> 00:46:12,200
I'm taking her to the hospital.
Notify the secretariat.

833
00:46:12,280 --> 00:46:15,160
